exercises.description:
Create a section that shows a CSS code example. Add an h3 'CSS Reset Example', then use <pre> and <code> to display this CSS code with proper formatting:
* {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
}
Below the code block, add a paragraph saying 'Apply this by adding it to your <code>styles.css</code> file.' (the filename should be in an inline <code> element).
